<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC "-//APACHE//DTD Documentation V2.0//EN"
"http://forrest.apache.org/dtd/document-v20.dtd">
<document xml:lang="se">
    <header>
        <title>Sajáiduhttit, heivehit ja molsut boallobevddiid Windows 10:s</title>
    </header>
    <body>
      <section>
      <title>Sajáiduhttin</title>
        <ol>
          <li>Mana <a
            href="http://divvun.no/no/keyboards/desktopindex.html">Divvuma
            siidui gos gávnnat boallobevddiid</a>, ja coahkkal
            <strong>Windows 10 viežžanliŋkka</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/01_download-sme-en.png"
            alt="Viežžan"/></p>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Vuoje</strong> sajáiduhtti maid vižžet:
            <p><img src="images/win10/02_run-installer-sme-en.png"
            alt="Vuoje sajáiduhtti"/></p>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Suova</strong> sajáiduhtti dahkat rievdadusaid:
            <p><img src="images/win10/03_allow_changes-sme-en.png"
            alt="Suova sajáiduhtti dahkat rievdadusaid"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Vállje sajáiduhtti giela:
            <p><img src="images/win10/04_select_inst_lang-sme-en.png"
            alt="Vállje sajáiduhtti giela"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Vállje gosa bidjá fiillaid. Ale rievdat jus eai
          leat erenoamáš dárbbut:
            <p><img src="images/win10/05_inst_location-sme-en.png"
            alt="Gosa bidjá fiillaid"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Vállje báikki <strong>Start</strong>-fálus. Ale rievdat jus eai
          leat erenoamáš dárbbut:
            <p><img src="images/win10/06_start_menu-sme-en.png"
            alt="Start menu"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Dál leat gárvvis sajáiduhttigoahtit:
            <p><img src="images/win10/07_ready_to_install-sme-en.png"
            alt="Gárvvis sajáiduhttigoahtit"/></p>
            <p><img src="images/win10/08_installing-sme-en.png"
            alt="Sajáiduhttin"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Ođđa boallobevddit doaibmagohtet albma láhkai easka maŋŋago
              leat <strong>vuolggahan dihtora ođđasit</strong>:
            <p><img src="images/win10/09_restart-sme-en.png"
                alt="Vuolggahit dihtora ođđasit"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Maŋŋágo dihtor lea ođđasit vuolggahuvvon, ođđa boallobeavddit
              galggašedje ihtit boallobeavdefálus (jus eai, čuovo bagadasa
              vuollelis):
            <p><img src="images/win10/10_keyboard_menu-sme-en.png"
            alt="Boallobeavdefállu"/></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      <section>
      <title>Heivehus</title>
        <p>Sajáiduhtti dábálaččat heiveha ođđa sajáiduvvon boallobevddiid.
            Jus dát ii leat dáhpáhuvvan, dahje jus háliidat rievdadit heivehusa,
            daga ná:</p>

        <ol>
          <li>Mana <strong>Start</strong>-fállui ja coahkkal
              <strong>heivehusaid</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/start_menu-no.png" alt="Startmeny"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Mana <strong>Tid og språk</strong>-merkošii:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-no.png" alt="Kontrollpanel"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Coahkkal <strong>Legg til et språk</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-time_and_lang-no.png"
              alt="Giella" /></p>
          </li>
          <li>Coahkkal <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-no.png"
              alt="Lasit giela"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Vállje dan <strong>Davvisámegieleavttu</strong> mii heive dutnje:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-norway-no.png"
              alt="Báikkálaš molssaeavttut"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Merke <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong> ja coahkkal
              <strong>Alternativer</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-modify-sme-no.png"
              alt="Giella maŋŋágo lea válljen davvisámegiela"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Coahkkal <strong>Legg til et tastatur</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-keyboard-no.png"
              alt="Giellamolssaeavttut"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Vállje <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-extended-norway-no.png"
              alt="Čállingiellavuohki"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Merke <strong>Norsk med samisk</strong> ja coahkkal
              <strong>Fjern</strong>:
              <p><img
              src="images/win10/prefs-remove-norw_with_sami-keyboard-no.png"
              alt="Giellamolssaeavttut: Váldde eret «norsk med samisk»"/></p>
          </li>
          <li>Dál dus lea <strong>Davvisámegiella (Norga)</strong> čállingiellan
              ja boallobeavdi mii gullá dasa lea <strong>Samisk, utvidet
              Norge</strong>:
              <p><img src="images/win10/keyboard-done-sme-no.png"
              alt="Giella go davvisámegiella lea heivehuvvon"/></p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
      <section>
      <title>Molsut boallobeavddi</title>
        <p>
          Boallobeavddis deaddilat
          <strong>Windows+gaska</strong> dassáigo davvisámi boallobeavdi lea
          aktiiva:
        </p>
        <p><img src="images/win10/switching-keyboards-sme-no.png"
          alt="Giella go davvisámegiella lea heivehuvvon"/></p>
      </section>
    </body>
</document>
